title: Requiem for a Heavyweight (TV, 1956) Kim Hunter Jack Palance
description:
This is the ORIGINAL version of the famous story about a boxer who has talen so many hits that he's almost no good for anything any more. The gritty feel of a live-to-air teleplay suits this story about boxing-ring backstage.  

"Jack Palance gives the finest performance of his career"... "This was a watershed production for American Television" -Reb9, IMDb.

In segmented mpg format, plays on VLC.
